ates Men Basketball Squad 1991 Pan American Games}}\n{{1994 NBA Draft}}\n{{NBA Rookies of the Year}}\n{{NBA Sportsmanship Award Winners}}\n{{IBM Award}}\n{{Footer 1996 Olympic Champions Basketball Men}}\n{{1991 Duke Blue Devils men's basketball navbox}}\n{{1992 Duke Blue Devils men's basketball navbox}}\n{{1993 NCAA Men's Basketball Consensus All-Americans}}\n{{1994 NCAA Men's Basketball Consensus All-Americans}}\n{{NABC Defensive Player of the Year}}\n{{Atlantic Coast Conference Men's Basketball Player of the Year navbox}}\n{{NBA on TNT}}\n{{2018 Basketball HOF}}\n{{Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame}}\n{{NCAA Gerald R. Ford Award}}\n}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hill, Grant}}\n[[Category:1972 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:African-American basketball players]]\n[[Category:All-American college men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:American art collectors]]\n[[Category:American men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Atlanta Hawks owners]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1991 NCAA Men's Division I Final Four]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1991 Pan American Games]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1992 NCAA Men's Division I Final Four]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1994 NCAA Men's Division I Final Four]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Basketball players from Texas]]\n[[Category:Basketball players from Virginia]]\n[[Category:College basketball announcers in the United States]]\n[[Category:Detroit Pistons draft picks]]\n[[Category:Detroit Pistons players]]\n[[Category:Duke Blue Devils men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Clippers players]]\n[[Category:McDonald's High School All-Americans]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:National Basketball Association All-Stars]]\n[[Category:National Collegiate Basketball Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:Olympic